body.description: Having a difficult time finding the right pacifier for your baby? The NUK Value Pack provides 3 different pacifiers in one package. Like all NUK pacifiers, the Value Pack features the improved NUK orthodontic nipple shape. Invented over 60 years ago by pediatric dentists and doctors, the NUK pacifier is modeled after the natural shape of mom’s nipple while breastfeeding. This makes for an easy transition from breast to pacifier and back. The asymmetrical nipple naturally fits baby’s palate and is now improved to allow for more room for a natural sucking motion, reduce pressure on teeth and jaw, and helps prevent teeth misalignment. The NUK heart-shaped shield fits perfectly under baby’s nose for easier breathing and prevents irritation. With a convenient glow-in-the-dark feature to help you find lost a pacifier during the night, this pack of 3 orthodontic pacifiers is ideal for your child aged 6-18 months. (*Based on Market Research, 2017, tested with 307 pacifier users).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Game changing glow in the dark pacifiers
reviews.reviewText: We recently purchased these glow in the dark pacifiers and I'm thrilled! We all know the stress of showering the bed with our hands in the dark to try to find that damned pacifier… we’ll this solves it all!The glow is soft and soothing, not overpowering or distracting during nighttime feedings or naps. It's the perfect level of brightness to provide comfort without disrupting sleep.The design is adorable, and the quality is excellent. The pacifiers are made of safe, high-quality materials that put my mind at ease. The orthodontic shape is great for my baby's oral development, too.Highly recommend for parents struggling to find their baby’s pacifier at night, and once they’re old enough, your little ones can find it in their own too!
